---
# LinApple .clang-tidy configuration
#
# This project favors a procedural, C-like C++11 style as mandated in AGENTS.md.
# We utilize the following exclusions from standard C++ Core Guidelines:
#
# 1. pro-type-vararg & avoid-variadic-functions:
#    Favoring printf-style formatting over iostream for performance, 
#    conciseness in hex-formatting, and C99 ABI compatibility.
#
# 2. avoid-non-const-global-variables:
#    Global hardware state (CPU, Memory, Registers) is a core design 
#    pattern in this emulator's procedural architecture.

Checks: 'google-*,bugprone-*,modernize-*,cppcoreguidelines-*,-cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-vararg,-modernize-avoid-variadic-functions,-cppcoreguidelines-avoid-non-const-global-variables'
WarningsAsErrors: ''
HeaderFilterRegex: ''
